snippet.title: Neophyte: The Journey Begins
snippet.description:
Lets's play Neophyte: The Journey Begins! At the end of the game, I became invulnerable, I considered that a bug or a game preference (maybe I reached the max level), because I didn't use cheats or trainers. However, the game can be done with the same moves without invulnerability. This is a shareware game, full version never released, so it has only one level.
Download link:
http://www.interactivitiesink.com/aliensoft/neophyte/home.html
